20世纪中期[[流行音乐|流行音乐]]和[[摇滚音乐|摇滚音乐]]兴起，影响到法国音乐界，出现[[香颂|香颂]]音乐。英语流行歌曲在国内受到欢迎，而香颂歌曲同样有着很高的知名度。著名的音乐人有[[艾迪特·皮雅芙|艾迪特·皮雅芙]]、{{le|乔治·布拉桑|Georges Brassens}}、{{le|莱奥·费雷|Léo Ferré}}、[[夏尔·阿兹纳武尔|夏尔·阿兹纳武尔]]和[[赛日·甘斯布|赛日·甘斯布]]。与英语国家相比，法国的摇滚音乐人相对较少<ref>RFI Musique, [http://www.rfimusic.com/artist/rock/noir-desir/biography Biography of Noir Désir] {{Wayback|url=http://www.rfimusic.com/artist/rock/noir-desir/biography |date=20160430102257 }}, March 2009: "Rock music doesn't come naturally to the French. A Latin country, with more affinity to poetry and melody, France has very rarely produced talented rock musicians. Rock music has other, more Anglo-Saxon ingredients"</ref>，但一些著名的乐队如{{le|Noir Désir|Noir Désir}}、{{le|Mano Negra|Mano Negra}}、{{le|Niagara (乐队)|Niagara (band)|Niagara}}、{{le|Les Rita Mitsouko|Les Rita Mitsouko}}、{{le|凤凰 (乐队)|Phoenix (band)|凤凰}}、[[Superbus|Superbus]]、{{le|Gojira|Gojira (band)}}仍在世界有着广泛知名度<ref name="frmusic">France Diplomatie, [http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/france_159/culture-and-media_6819/culture_6874/music_5335/french-music-has-the-whole-planet-singing_13031.html French music has the whole planet singing] {{Wayback|url=http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/france_159/culture-and-media_6819/culture_6874/music_5335/french-music-has-the-whole-planet-singing_13031.html |date=20101222105333 }}, June 2009</ref>。许多法国歌手于国内外都有着较高人气，如[[黛莉達|黛莉達]]、[[米蕾耶·玛蒂厄|米蕾耶·玛蒂厄]]、[[米莲·法莫|米莲·法莫]]<ref name=frmusic />和{{le|诺尔韦恩·勒鲁瓦|Nolwenn Leroy}}<ref>{{fr icon}} [http://www.irma.asso.fr/IMG/pdf/bureauexport_dossierdepresse_2013_fr.pdf "Bureau Export – Les certifications export 2012"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.irma.asso.fr/IMG/pdf/bureauexport_dossierdepresse_2013_fr.pdf |date=20160804030646 }}. IRMA. p.26. Retrieved 7 March 2015.</ref>等女歌手；[[电子音乐|电子音乐]]的先驱[[让-米歇尔·雅尔|让-米歇尔·雅尔]]、{{le|洛朗·加尼耶|Laurent Garnier}}和{{le|鲍勃·桑克拉尔|Bob Sinclar}}，以及之后的[[唱片骑师|唱片骑师]]{{le|马丁·佐尔法伊格|Martin Solveig}}和[[大卫·库塔_(DJ)|大卫·库塔]]。近年来，电子音乐二人组合[[傻朋克|傻朋克]]、{{le|Justice (乐队)|Justice (band)|Justice}}和{{Le|Aie (法国乐队)|Air (French band)|Air}}亦拥有世界级人气，且为现代电子音乐的传播做出较大贡献<ref name=frmusic /><ref>The Telegraph, [http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/3669339/Daft-Punk-Behind-the-robot-masks.html Daft Punk: Behind the robot masks] {{Wayback|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/culture/music/3669339/Daft-Punk-Behind-the-robot-masks.html |date=20160415163421 }}, 17 November 2007: "Daft Punk were in many ways responsible for turning the spotlight on a new, cool underground of French music in the late 1990s, including bestselling acts such as Air, and have been a huge influence on the current generation of international star DJs"</ref><ref>{{Cite news |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1721450.stm |title=The return of French pop music |date=2001-12-20 |publisher=BBC News |accessdate=2011-07-22 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511103812/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/entertainment/1721450.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

法国许多现有的音乐活动和机构皆致力于古典音乐和歌剧的演出，例如著名的[[国立巴黎歌剧团|国立巴黎歌剧团]]（主要演出场地是[[巴黎歌剧院|巴黎歌剧院]]和[[巴士底歌剧院|巴士底歌剧院]]），{{le|里昂国家歌剧团|Opéra National de Lyon}}，巴黎的[[夏特雷劇院|夏特雷劇院]]，图卢兹的[[市政厅剧院|市政厅剧院]]和[[波尔多大剧院|波尔多大剧院]]。著名的音乐节有{{le|欧洲摇滚节|Eurockéennes}}和{{Le|塞纳河摇滚节|Rock en Seine}}两个[[摇滚音乐|摇滚音乐]]节，以及源于法国、众多国家一同庆祝的[[世界音樂節|世界音樂節]]，于1982年由法国政府设立<ref>Ministry of Culture of France, [http://www.fetedelamusique.culture.fr/site-2010/?page_id=550 About "Fête de la Musique"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.fetedelamusique.culture.fr/site-2010/?page_id=550 |date=20100515071351 }}</ref><ref>France Diplomatie, [http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/france_159/culture-and-media_6819/culture_6874/music_5335/fete-musique-21 June 2007_9392.html Fête de la Musique] {{Wayback|url=http://www.diplomatie.gouv.fr/en/france_159/culture-and-media_6819/culture_6874/music_5335/fete-musique-21 |date=20120118060250 }}, 21 June 2007</ref>。其它著名的音乐厅有分布于众多城市的{{le|顶点剧场|Le Zénith}}，以及巴黎的[[奥林匹亚音乐厅|奥林匹亚音乐厅]]、[[莫加多尔剧院|莫加多尔剧院]]和{{le|蒙马特爱丽舍剧场|Élysée Montmartre}}等。

